   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To my lord brother Theodoros, administrator, Phoibammon very good health and very many greetings. Give to Olympios, adiutor e commentariis for my account two hundred myriads of silver (denarii). total 200 myr. den. only. I pray for your health througth many years. Year 86 = 55, Mesore 16.</ab>
         </div>
